Created 2 additional volumes/disks of 10G and 12 G(find me readme)

lsblk= to show all blocks
df -h = shows all mounts

we created 2 additional volumes/disks = physical volume (PVS)

lvm> pvcreate /dev/sdb /dev/sdc (to create physical volume)

root@Sandeep-linux:~# pvs
  PV         VG    Fmt  Attr PSize   PFree
  /dev/sdc   newvg lvm2 a--  <12.00g  <4.00g
  /dev/sdd   newvg lvm2 a--  <10.00g <10.00g
root@Sandeep-linux:~#

lvm> vgcreate newvg /dev/sdb /dev/sdc

We add 10G and 12G and make a volume group(VGS)
root@Sandeep-linux:~# vgs
  VG    #PV #LV #SN Attr   VSize  VFree
  newvg   2   1   0 wz--n- 21.99g 13.99g
root@Sandeep-linux:~#
lvm>lvcreate -L 8G -n lvnew newvg

We divide the volume into segment and mount where we need(lvs):

root@Sandeep-linux:~# lvs
  LV    VG    Attr       LSize Pool Origin Data%  Meta%  Move Log Cpy%Sync Convert
  lvnew newvg -wi-ao---- 8.00g
root@Sandeep-linux:~#

root@Sandeep-linux:~# lsblk
