mounting disk to azure linux:
mkfs -t ext4 <path>

Let's make logicalk volume more 5gb if storage is going to be full dynamically

lvm> lvextend -L +5G /dev/newvg/lvnew
  Size of logical volume newvg/lvnew changed from 8.00 GiB (2048 extents) to 13.00 GiB (3328 extents).
  Logical volume newvg/lvnew successfully resized.
lvm>
